---
title: Tempura Fish Tacos with Avocado Crema & Cabbage-Radish Slaw
description: Airy rice flour and seltzer create a light and crispy batter for these Old Bay-spiced fish tacos. Luscious avocado serves double duty as both a taco filling and creamy slaw dressing. Crispy radish and cabbage add the perfect crunch, while lime finishes off the dish with a pop of acidity.
